article.description: — Josh Caldwell had 14 points and seven rebounds as Army romped past Merrimack 74-51 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Caldwell scores 14 to carry Army over Merrimack 74-51
article.linkText: Caldwell scores 14 to carry Army over Merrimack 74-51
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. -- — Josh Caldwell had 14 points and seven rebounds as Army romped past Merrimack 74-51 on Wednesday night. Charlie Peterson had 13 points for Army (3-1). Jared Cross added 11 points. Jalen Rucker had seven rebounds. Mykel Derring had 11 points and five steals for the Warriors (2-2). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
